Package: adsb-history-logger
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3
Description: Local, unfiltered ADS-B position history logger
 Connects to a dump1090-fa/readsb SBS feed and records position history for
 every aircraft seen into a local SQLite database, independent of any
 external aggregator's filtering (e.g. FAA LADD/PIA privacy programs).
 Includes a query CLI for per-aircraft visit history, track export, and
 registration/type search, a retention pruning job, and an optional
 tar1090 integration that adds a "History" panel to the aircraft info
 sidebar for viewing and drawing past tracks on the live map.
